org.cpsolver.studentsct.online.selection

Class StudentSchedulingAssistantWeights

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.studentsct.online.selection.StudentSchedulingAssistantWeights
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SolutionComparator<Request,Enrollment>, StudentWeights
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ResectioningWeights

    public class StudentSchedulingAssistantWeights
extends Object
implements StudentWeights
    Online variant of StudentWeights model. It is either based on PriorityStudentWeights (when StudentWeights.PriorityWeighting=true) or on EqualStudentWeights. Following criteria are included:
    • StudentWeights.NoTimeFactor .. penalization of sections with no time assigned (arrange hours)
    • StudentWeights.SelectionFactor .. penalization of sections that are not selected (if there are selected sections given for a course request, see CourseRequest.getSelectedChoices())
    • StudentWeights.PenaltyFactor .. penalization for over-expected sections (using OverExpectedCriterion.getOverExpected(Assignment, Section, Request)
    • StudentWeights.AvgPenaltyFactor .. penalization of section penalties (see Section.getPenalty()), using average penalty per request
    • StudentWeights.AvailabilityFactor .. penalization of unbalanced sections (portion of the section over the target fill, averaged per request)
    Version:
    StudentSct 1.3 (Student Sectioning)
